These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, grapes
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, bike
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person eating raspberry is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | raspberry   | grapes   |
| Transport   | bike | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, baseball
1. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
2. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | tea | iced-tea   |
| Sport      | baseball | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, corn
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, ambient
1. the person eating raspberry is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
2. the person eating corn is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | corn | raspberry |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | ambient     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
